text: Clarita Heath (August 27, 1916 - October 13, 2003) was an American alpine skier. She competed in the women's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1916 births Category:2003 deaths Category:American female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of the United States Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Pasadena, California
